
                                   ; Alpha Character display code
                                   ; Guy Fedorkow
                                   ; Nov 21, 2025; Mar 7, 2026
                                   ; This program displays a simple text message on the WW CRT display
                                   ; The text of the message is one of eight messages, selected by the low three bits
                                   ; of FF Register 2

                                   ; Modified Apr 19, 2026 to position the message in the center of the screen
                                   ; Modified Apr 19, 2026 to make descenders on g, j, p, y, q


